      <title>Houthi攻击停顿让欧洲现在通过Suez获得更多的燃料</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/houthi-attack-pause-lets-europe-get-more-fuel-via-suez-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[胡塞（Houthi）对商业运输的袭击中的停顿使燃料交易员通过埃及的苏伊士运河将更多的货物进口到欧洲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/houthi-attack-pause-lets-europe-get-more-fuel-via-suez-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 09:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
