      <title>BP以10亿美元的价格将天然气管道股份出售给阿波罗资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/apollo-funds-to-buy-25-stake-in-bp-tanap-for-about-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BP PLC表示，由阿波罗管理的资金将购买BP Pipelines的25％非控制股份＆Mdash;被称为bp tanap＆mdash;大约有10亿美元，标志着这家英国能源巨头在其周转计划下的首次撤资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/apollo-funds-to-buy-25-stake-in-bp-tanap-for-about-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 08:48:46 GMT</pubDate>
