    <item>
      <title>卢比头在两年内最好的一周，随着流入恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/rupee-heads-for-best-week-in-two-years-as-inflows-resume</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2023年1月以来，印度的卢比（India）的卢比（Rupee）正处于最佳的一周之久，外国基金流入了当地债券和股市反弹，这引起了投资者的情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/rupee-heads-for-best-week-in-two-years-as-inflows-resume</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 08:35:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
